NAME
    MetaPOD::Format::JSON - Reference implementation of a "JSON" based
    MetaPOD Format

VERSION
    version 0.2.5

SYNOPSIS
    This is the reference implementation of "MetaPOD::JSON"

METHODS
  "supported_versions"
    The versions this module supports

        returns qw( v1.0.0 v1.1.0 )

  "add_segment"
    See "::Role::Format" for the specification of the "add_segment" method.

